      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six and its signature individual throttle bodies. The VANOS system has been professionally serviced, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure structural rigidity under high torque loads. Power is delivered through a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission that provides crisp, tactile engagement. The chassis remains composed thanks to refreshed bushings and a well-sorted suspension geometry. While showing minor aesthetic road wear, the drivetrain and cooling system are in excellent working order, making this a performance-ready specimen for the discerning purist.",
