      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 Toyota 4Runner TRD Off-Road that perfectly balances rugged utility with everyday comfort. The exterior is finished in a striking Classic Silver Metallic that retains a deep gloss; while you will find a few minor stone chips on the leading edge of the hood from highway travel, the body panels are remarkably straight and free of any significant dings. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in. The black SofTex upholstery is supple with no visible tears, and the carpets have been protected by all-weather mats since day one. Every feature, from the crawl control dials to the touchscreen navigation and heated seats, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, this SUV is in prime health with a documented history of synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles. The transmission shifts seamlessly, the brakes were recently serviced, and the BFGoodrich tires offer substantial tread for many miles to come. This is a solid, honest vehicle ready for its next owner to take it off the beaten path or on a cross-country tour.",
